in the world.

519
00:37:56,903 --> 00:37:58,336
How well did you know my mother?

520
00:38:02,375 --> 00:38:07,403
We enjoyed each other's company.

521
00:38:07,847 --> 00:38:09,781
Bernice and I.

522
00:38:09,949 --> 00:38:12,747
Dex wasn't too thrilled.

523
00:38:13,319 --> 00:38:16,015
