527
00:38:30,670 --> 00:38:33,070
He tried to kill me.

528
00:38:34,140 --> 00:38:36,131
I had to defend myself.

529
00:38:39,212 --> 00:38:43,672
Why didn't you tell me
instead of this insane charade? Why?

530
00:38:43,916 --> 00:38:48,148
The garden is filled with lies, Harry.

531
00:38:48,921 --> 00:38:50,445
Little lies.

532
00:38:50,623 --> 00:38:55,959
Thousands over a lifetime,
like lilies of the field.

533
00:38:56,896 --> 00:39:01,299
My lies are Mimecom's.

534
00:39:01,467 --> 00:39:04,334
State-of-the-art, for the masses.

535
00:39:05,938 --> 00:39:08,168
You took Peter...

536
00:39:08,608 --> 00:39:11,441
...my son, away from me.

537
00:39:11,744 --> 00:39:15,840
You took everything from me
that I loved.

538
00:39:16,449 --> 00:39:17,848
Tell me why.

539
00:39:18,317 --> 00:39:23,584
Do you know what the unicorn does
when it's surrounded by hunters?

540
00:39:23,756 --> 00:39:25,849
Tell me why,
you psychotic son of a bitch.

541
00:39:26,025 --> 00:39:30,189
