breaking the fall with its horn.

542
00:39:30,496 --> 00:39:32,123
You destroyed Coty.

543
00:39:32,298 --> 00:39:33,993
Your brother, Coty.

544
00:39:34,166 --> 00:39:36,930
It's rather like an Arabian tale,
isn't it, Harry?

545
00:39:37,103 --> 00:39:39,571
You made a monster out of that boy!

546
00:39:43,910 --> 00:39:46,003
What's happening?

547
00:39:48,948 --> 00:39:50,210
Oh, my God.

548
00:39:53,886 --> 00:39:56,218
We altered the chip.

549
00:39:56,789 --> 00:39:58,814
Peter and I.

550
00:39:58,991 --> 00:40:00,390
My son.

551
00:40:01,394 --> 00:40:03,692
If there was time...

552
00:40:03,863 --> 00:40:08,129
...I would tell you all
about your mother and me.

553
00:40:08,301 --> 00:40:12,635
I would tell you things
only the wild palms know.

554
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,632
Can't feel my legs.

555
00:40:15,808 --> 00:40:18,436
Ain't that the craziest thing?

556
00:40:18,611 --> 00:40:21,307
<i>Hello
I must be going</i>

557
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:25,109
<i>I cannot stay
I came to say, I must be going</i>

558
00:40:25,284 --> 00:40:27,912
Don't you leave. Not yet!

559
00:40:30,323 --> 00:40:33,315
<i>I'm glad I came, but just the same</i>

560
00:40:33,492 --> 00:40:36,655
<i>- I must be going
- You ruined everything.</i>

561
00:40:36,829 --> 00:40:39,662
You ruined everything
that you touched.

562
00:40:39,832 --> 00:40:42,266
What's the matter?
Wasn't this world enough for you?

563
00:40:42,768 --> 00:40:45,202
<i>I'll stay a week or two</i>

564
00:40:45,371 --> 00:40:47,464
You didn't have to run to paradise...

565
00:40:48,007 --> 00:40:50,032
...Father!

566
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:53,635
Paradise is here!

567
00:40:54,413 --> 00:40:56,779
Here, damn it! Here!

568
00:40:56,949 --> 00:40:59,042
Paradise is right here!

569
00:40:59,218 --> 00:41:01,118
<i>I'll stay the summer through</i>

570
00:41:01,287 --> 00:41:03,482
<i>But I am telling you</i>

571
00:41:03,656 --> 00:41:07,752
<i>I must be going</i>

572
00:41:07,994 --> 00:41:09,723
