Harry, look!

578
00:41:46,899 --> 00:41:48,389
Did you speak to Father?

579
00:41:48,834 --> 00:41:50,802
- In the living room.
- Living room?

580
00:41:50,970 --> 00:41:53,734
Funny, his body's
in the guesthouse.

581
00:41:54,140 --> 00:41:56,404
You know,
I talked to him a while too.

582
00:41:56,575 --> 00:41:59,772
Then he floated over the roof
like a Chagall.

583
00:41:59,945 --> 00:42:01,310
It's over now.

584
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:03,846
Easy for you to say.

585
00:42:04,050 --> 00:42:06,450
- Hello, Mother.
- Coty, let us go.

586
00:42:07,153 --> 00:42:09,713
You're very James Bond today,
Mother.

587
00:42:09,889 --> 00:42:11,982
She was always
in awe of Pussy Galore.

588
00:42:13,259 --> 00:42:14,851
Hey, stay away!

589
00:42:16,529 --> 00:42:18,554
All this time...

590
