600
00:42:44,990 --> 00:42:47,083
How poignant.

601
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:49,257
What are you gonna do, Coty?
Kill us all?

602
00:42:49,428 --> 00:42:52,488
Deirdre's watching.
What do you think she sees?

603
00:42:52,832 --> 00:42:54,459
You think she wants to
stay with you?

604
00:42:54,633 --> 00:42:55,998
Hey, she loves me.

605
00:42:56,168 --> 00:42:59,433
The great child guru of Synthiotics,
a monster.

606
00:42:59,605 --> 00:43:00,970
How can she love a monster?

607
