624
00:43:57,863 --> 00:43:59,558
Daddy!

625
00:43:59,732 --> 00:44:01,427
Come here, baby.

626
00:44:01,600 --> 00:44:03,295
Come here.

627
00:44:05,471 --> 00:44:08,167
